import View from './View.js'; import icons from '../../img/icons.svg'; class RecipeView extends View { _parentElement = document.querySelector('.recipe'); _errorMessage = 'We could not find that recipe. Please try another one!'; _message = ''; _generateMarkup() { return `
${ this._data.cookingTime } minutes
${ this._data.servings } servings

Recipe ingredients

    ${this._data.ingredients .map(ing => { return `
  • ${ ing.quantity ? ing.quantity : '' }
    ${ing.unit} ${ing.description}
    • `; }) .join('')}

How to cook it

This recipe was carefully designed and tested by ${ this._data.publisher }. Please check out directions at their website.

Directions
`; } addHandlerRender(handler) { ['hashchange', 'load'].forEach(event => window.addEventListener(event, handler) ); } } export default new RecipeView();
